betterquesting:10.desc:8:
§7§oWoot mobfarms work by repeating the same loot of the first 100 kills of a given mob.

Because of this, if a mob has rare loot, it is possible that what you are looking for will not show up.

If that happens you can use this item to reset ALL Woot pools.

Since this does it for every woot farm, it may cause lag if you have lots of Woot farms currently running.
